## 4. Notificações em Tempo Real (SSE)

**Rota:** `GET /sse/orders` — middleware `auth`

### Backend
```php
// OrderSseController@stream
return response()->stream(function () {
    while (true) {
        $count = Order::query()
            ->where('store_id', auth()->user()->store_id)
            ->where('status', 'pending')
            ->where('notified_at', null)
            ->count();

        if ($count > 0) {
            echo "data: " . json_encode(['count' => $count]) . "\n\n";
        }

        ob_flush();
        flush();
        sleep(8);
    }
}, 200, [
    'Content-Type'      => 'text/event-stream',
    'Cache-Control'     => 'no-cache',
    'X-Accel-Buffering' => 'no',
]);
```

### Frontend (jQuery + SSE nativo)
```js
// Arquivo: public/js/orders/notifications.js
(function () {
  const audio = new Audio('/sounds/notify.mp3');
  audio.volume = 0.35;

  const source = new EventSource('/sse/orders');

  source.onmessage = function (e) {
    const data = JSON.parse(e.data);
    if (data.count > 0) {
      $('#order-notification-badge').text(data.count).removeClass('hidden');
      audio.play().catch(() => {}); // catch: autoplay policy
    }
  };

  source.onerror = function () {
    // EventSource reconecta automaticamente — não é necessário intervir
  };

  $('#order-notification-badge').on('click', function () {
    window.location.href = '/orders?status=pending';
  });
})();
```

**Notas:**
- Arquivo de som: `public/sounds/notify.mp3` — tom curto e suave (< 1s)
- Badge no Navbar: `<span id="order-notification-badge" class="hidden">0</span>`
- Sem Redis, Pusher ou Echo

