## Modelos e relações esperadas
```php
// Order
- belongsTo: Customer, Store, User (assigned_to), User (separator_id)
- hasMany: OrderItems, OrderStatusHistories
- casts: status (enum OrderStatus), fulfillment_type (enum FulfillmentType)

// OrderItem
- belongsTo: Order, ProductVariation
- attributes: qty, unit_price, subtotal

// OrderStatusHistory
- belongsTo: Order, User (changed_by)
- attributes: from_status, to_status, note, created_at
```

